```
# Java/Maven build artifacts
target/
*.class
*.jar
*.war
*.ear

# Dependencies
lib/
!lib/**/*

# IDE files
.idea/
*.iml
*.ipr
*.iws
.vscode/

# Logs
*.log

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.temp
*.bak

# Environment
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Coverage reports
coverage/
htmlcov/
.coverage

# System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Python artifacts (if any Python in project)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
*.py~
.Python
```